---

<section class="history-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="history-layout">
      <div class="history-content">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        
        <div class="history-text">
          <p>
            What began in the 1970s as a family initiative has blossomed into a transformative movement. 
            Our founders envisioned a way to share Ecuador's rich cultural heritage while creating sustainable 
            opportunities for local communities.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Today, we operate across 40+ communities, employing over 200 people and generating meaningful 
            economic impact without compromising our core values of environmental stewardship and cultural 
            preservation. Each experience we offer is designed to benefit the communities we work with, 
            ensuring that tourism becomes a force for good.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Recognized by UNESCO for our cultural conservation efforts, we continue to innovate in sustainable 
            tourism while maintaining deep roots in local traditions. Our commitment extends beyond tourism – 
            we're building a legacy of equity, respect, and shared prosperity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="history-stats">
        <div class="history-stat">
          <div class="stat-number">50+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Years</div>
        </div>
        <div class="history-stat">
          <div class="stat-number">40+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Communities</div>
        </div>
        <div class="history-stat">
          <div class="stat-number">200+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Jobs Created</div>
        </div>
        <div class="history-stat">
          <div class="stat-number">UNESCO</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Heritage Site</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .history-section {
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    background: white;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .history-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2D5016;
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
  }

  .history-text p {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .history-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .history-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .history-stat {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f5 0%, #efefef 100%);
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    transition: all 300ms ease;
  }

  .history-stat:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2D5016 0%, #1f3610 100%);
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(45, 80, 22, 0.2);
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2D5016;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .history-stat:hover .stat-number {
    color: white;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #8B7355;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .history-stat:hover .stat-label {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .history-layout {
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .history-section {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .history-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .history-text p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .history-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .history-stat {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
  }
</style>
